title: Skinned.launcher problems. Won't even open the league of legends starting setup.
body: So, when I open my league of legends at the garena, normally it will open the starting league of legends. But I don't , it says "League of legends SKINNED.LAUNCHER has encountered a problem and needs to close. We are sorry for the inconvenience." It's a error, i have no idea what to do. This is my first time encountering this problem. Can somebody help with this? Any ideas?

replies.body:
Unfortunately, Riot doesn't operate or support the Garena client. You'll need to reach out to [Garena Support](http://support.lol.garena.com/en_SG) for assistance.

Let me know if you have any questions.
